video.title: Saved by the Bell
video.synopsis: Bayside High is the spot for tons of fun, romance and even a little education for best friends Zack, Kelly, Slater, Jessie, Screech and Lisa.

episodes.synopsis: Eighth-grader Zack runs into a ninth-grader he met during the summer -- and lied to about his age.
episodes.title: Summer Love

episodes.synopsis: Complications of the romantic kind arise when Miss Bliss intercepts a love note intended for Lisa.
episodes.title: Love Letters

episodes.synopsis: Zack bullishly hopes he can make enough money on the stock market to pay for damages done to his father's VCR.
episodes.title: Wall Street

episodes.synopsis: A student's refusal to dissect a frog in biology class sparks a controversy among her peers.
episodes.title: Leaping to Conclusions

episodes.synopsis: Zack won't admit it, but he's disturbed by the chemistry between his father and his teacher.
episodes.title: Parents and Teachers

episodes.synopsis: The gang encourages Screech to stand up to a bully, unaware of the reason behind the boy's tough exterior.
episodes.title: The Showdown

episodes.synopsis: At a school mixer, Zack encourages a friend to ask a girl to dance -- but the girl would rather dance with Zack.
episodes.title: Save the Last Dance for Me

episodes.synopsis: Principal Belding smells a rat when the school is plagued by rodents just as Zack is due to take an important midterm.
episodes.title: The Boy Who Cried Rat

episodes.synopsis: An argument among students over a class project helps Miss Bliss clear up her differences with a longtime friend.
episodes.title: Let's Get Together

episodes.synopsis: Screech is "tried" for pulling a prank on Miss Bliss.
episodes.title: Practical Jokes

episodes.synopsis: Zack bets he can plant a kiss on a pop singer who's giving her final performance at school before going on to college.
episodes.title: Stevie

episodes.synopsis: Anxious to click with a cool campus clique, Zack agrees to insult his friends -- unaware that he's the victim of a prank.
episodes.title: Clubs and Cliques

episodes.synopsis: Principal Belding disapproves of the unconventional teacher substituting for Miss Bliss's history class.
episodes.title: The Mentor

episodes.synopsis: A national dance contest is held at the Max, and the whole gang decides to enter -- with mixed results.
episodes.title: Dancing to the Max

episodes.synopsis: When Lisa spends too much on her father's credit card, the kids sell Lisa's clothes to raise money to pay him back.
episodes.title: The Lisa Card

episodes.synopsis: Screech gets struck by lightning and is temporarily able to foretell the future.
episodes.title: The Gift

episodes.synopsis: Kelly has to choose between Zack and Slater to go to a big dance Bayside is having.
episodes.title: Fatal Distraction

episodes.synopsis: To help an ego-deflated Screech, Zack poses as Bambi, a girl with a crush on Screech.
episodes.title: Screech's Woman

episodes.synopsis: Slater's dad wants to move to Hawaii. Zack schemes to have all the kids be mean to him so he'll want to move and Zack will have Kelly all to himself.
episodes.title: Aloha Slater

episodes.synopsis: A handsome teacher substitutes for Miss Simpson, and all the girls fall for him.
episodes.title: The Substitute

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Screech think they've come up with a cure for zits when an experiment in science backfires.
episodes.title: Cream for a Day

episodes.synopsis: Zack bets a bully his dirt bike that Slater will win a wrestling match.
episodes.title: Pinned to the Mat

episodes.synopsis: When Screech tutors Kelly so that she can pass a midterm, she develops an unlikely crush on him, much to Zack and Slater's dismay.
episodes.title: Beauty and the Screech

episodes.synopsis: For a class project, the kids start a successful business selling friendship bracelets, until Zack develops a thirst for power and money.
episodes.title: The Friendship Business

episodes.synopsis: For a class project, the kids must act as married couples for a week.
episodes.title: The Mamas and the Papas

episodes.synopsis: Kelly breaks her arm, so the kids look after her baby brother -- at school!
episodes.title: The Baby Sitters

episodes.synopsis: When Zack discovers that the new student body president will win a trip to Washington, D.C., he runs against Jessie solely to win the trip.
episodes.title: The Election

episodes.synopsis: Zack puts subliminal messages on Kelly's rock tape to persuade her to ask him to dance.
episodes.title: The Zack Tapes

episodes.synopsis: This episode moves the gang from junior high to Bayside High School.
episodes.title: King of the Hill

episodes.synopsis: It's the homecoming game against Valley, and the two schools play their annual round of pranks.
episodes.title: Save That Tiger

episodes.synopsis: When the kids need to raise money to replace the school video camera, they enter a contest that gives a prize for the best photo of an alien.
episodes.title: Close Encounters of the Nerd Kind

episodes.synopsis: After his friends and parents forget his birthday, Screech takes out his revenge by becoming a tyrannical hall monitor.
episodes.title: Screech's Birthday

episodes.synopsis: After Slater's pet lizard dies while the kids are watching it, they try to replace it with another without Slater noticing.
episodes.title: Slater's Friend

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Slater vie to take Kelly to the prom, but Kelly might not be able to go at all when she finds out her father has lost his job.
episodes.title: The Prom

episodes.synopsis: An ROTC official comes to Bayside to recruit kids.
episodes.title: Zack's War

episodes.synopsis: The kids have a radio-thon to raise money to save the Max.
episodes.title: Save the Max

episodes.synopsis: The kids get a lesson in responsible driving.
episodes.title: Driver's Education

episodes.synopsis: Screech's parents go out of town and leave Screech and Zack alone in the house.
episodes.title: House Party

episodes.synopsis: Jessie and Zack both have blind dates.
episodes.title: Blind Dates

episodes.synopsis: Zack hires an actor to play his dad for a conference at school.
episodes.title: Rent-A-Pop

episodes.synopsis: Zack enters Screech in a Homecoming Queen contest.
episodes.title: Miss Bayside

episodes.synopsis: Jessie becomes hooked on caffeine pills to keep up with all of her activities.
episodes.title: Jessie's Song

episodes.synopsis: To make money, Zack sells calendars with pictures of the girls without their knowledge.
episodes.title: Model Students

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Slater get a 900 number and set up an advice hotline for teens.
episodes.title: 1-900 Crushed

episodes.synopsis: Zack deals with the death of a friend.
episodes.title: Running Zack

episodes.synopsis: Zack asks Kelly to go steady -- but he has a small change of heart when he meets the school nurse who's giving everyone flu shots.
episodes.title: From Nurse to Worse

episodes.synopsis: Belding's younger and hipper brother substitute teaches and breaks most of the rules to get on the kids' good side.
episodes.title: The Fabulous Belding Boys

episodes.synopsis: Jessie and Slater, Zack and Kelly, and Mr. and Mrs. Belding break up at the same time.
episodes.title: Breaking Up Is Hard to Undo

episodes.synopsis: The kids join the glee club in hopes of winning a contest and a trip to Hawaii.
episodes.title: The Glee Club

episodes.synopsis: Kelly and Zack break up when Kelly falls for the college-age manager of the Max.
episodes.title: The Last Dance

episodes.synopsis: Zack's friends set him up on numerous dates and he tries to make Kelly jealous. Lisa has her Sweet 16 party.
episodes.title: The Aftermath

episodes.synopsis: Zack is scared about having surgery on his knee. Lisa's mother performs the operation.
episodes.title: Operation Zack

episodes.synopsis: Screech wins a spot in the chess tournament finals against a Russian player.
episodes.title: Check Your Mate

episodes.synopsis: Zack, Screech and Slater make fake IDs to get into a club, where they discover Kelly's boyfriend with another girl.
episodes.title: Fake IDs

episodes.synopsis: Oil is found under Bayside. The community votes not to pump it so the natural balance of the land won't be destroyed.
episodes.title: Pipe Dreams

episodes.synopsis: Jessie's mother marries a man with a tough New York son. He blackmails Zack, who cuts school to go to a Dodgers game.
episodes.title: The Wicked Stepbrother: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Jessie's stepbrother falls for Lisa and continues to scheme against Zack and Slater.
episodes.title: The Wicked Stepbrother: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: A plus-size girl buys a date with Zack, who learns to overlook her weight.
episodes.title: Date Auction

episodes.synopsis: Zack and the gang try to scam the Stansbury College rep so she'll consider Jessie even though her SAT scores are too low.
episodes.title: SATs

episodes.synopsis: Zack helps a girl join the boys wrestling team.
episodes.title: Hold Me Tight

episodes.synopsis: A famous movie star comes to Bayside to film an antidrug PSA. He turns out to be a hypocrite who smokes pot.
episodes.title: No Hope with Dope

episodes.synopsis: Zack can't cut school on Cut Day because he has too many absences.
episodes.title: Cut Day

episodes.synopsis: Slater's other girlfriend from Germany transfers to Bayside.
episodes.title: Love Machine

episodes.synopsis: Zack shoots the yearbook video-style and sells the tapes of the prettiest girls to get money for a car.
episodes.title: The Video Yearbook

episodes.synopsis: The kids do a rap version of "Snow White" as the annual school play. Violet overcomes her shyness when she is cast as the lead singer.
episodes.title: Snow White and the Seven Dorks

episodes.synopsis: The kids start their jobs at the beach club and sneak in after hours to have a surprise birthday party for Zack.
episodes.title: Zack's Birthday Party

episodes.synopsis: The Malibu Beach Club plays a volleyball game against a rival. Zack finds a tall guy and promises him a date with Kelly so he'll play on the team.
episodes.title: The Game

episodes.synopsis: Zack must name the winner of the Miss Liberty Beauty pageant. The problem is that the contestants are Lisa, Jessie, Kelly and Stacey.
episodes.title: Fourth of July

episodes.synopsis: Stacey Carosi's college boyfriend shows up unexpectedly.
episodes.title: My Boyfriend's Back

episodes.synopsis: Carosi leaves Stacey in charge of the club and has mistakenly booked two parties for the same night. Zack helps Stacey out of the bind.
episodes.title: Boss Lady

episodes.synopsis: Stacey goes back to Boston; the kids wrap up their beach club jobs.
episodes.title: The Last Weekend

episodes.synopsis: The gang finds $5,000 at the mall. Zack decides to "invest" the money in concert tickets and turn a profit before returning the money.
episodes.title: All in the Mall

episodes.synopsis: The kids go to a resort in Palm Springs for Jessie's father's wedding. Slater meets a princess from another country.
episodes.title: Palm Springs Weekend: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Jessie tries to stop the wedding. Slater tells the princess he can't see her anymore.
episodes.title: Palm Springs Weekend: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Zack has a fantasy that the group becomes famous rock stars.
episodes.title: Rockumentary

episodes.synopsis: Zack finds out the girl he likes, Laura, is homeless. She and her dad move into Zack's house temporarily.
episodes.title: Home for Christmas: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The group helps Laura and her father get back on their feet.
episodes.title: Home for Christmas: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: The gang spends the weekend at a murder mystery mansion. Zack winds up as the accused murderer and must get himself off the hook.
episodes.title: Mystery Weekend

episodes.synopsis: A pretty transfer student from Idaho leads Zack and Slater to come to blows over who will date her.
episodes.title: The Fight

episodes.synopsis: Kids and teachers switch places.
episodes.title: Student-Teacher Week

episodes.synopsis: On a cable access show, the kids sell Screech's grandmother's spaghetti sauce.
episodes.title: Screech's Spaghetti Sauce

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Lisa fall for each other. Screech is upset and almost ruins Lisa's fashion show.
episodes.title: The Bayside Triangle

episodes.synopsis: A.C. and Maj. Slater fight over where A.C. should attend college. Jessie becomes a cheerleader.
episodes.title: Wrestling with the Future

episodes.synopsis: This clips show looks back at romantic moments.
episodes.title: Isn't It Romantic?

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Slater egg on a teachers' strike, until they find out their academic championship will be canceled as a result.
episodes.title: The Teacher's Strike

episodes.synopsis: The kids can't afford a regular senior prom so they have a Western dance.
episodes.title: The Senior Prom

episodes.synopsis: Kids at Bayside in 2003 find a video left by the gang in 1993 in this flashback episode set in the future.
episodes.title: The Time Capsule

episodes.synopsis: Zack is one credit short of graduation, and Jessie worries about being valedictorian.
episodes.title: Graduation

episodes.synopsis: A tough new girl from Chicago irritates Zack and then falls for him.
episodes.title: The New Girl

episodes.synopsis: Zack learns a valuable lesson when the kids set up a "teen-line" at Bayside in order to counsel kids with problems.
episodes.title: Teen-Line

episodes.synopsis: Zack and Slater make a bet about who can kiss Tori first.
episodes.title: Masquerade Ball

episodes.synopsis: Everyone ends up spending a day in detention.
episodes.title: Day of Detention

episodes.synopsis: Everyone celebrates Lisa's victory as Bayside's new homecoming queen at a party.
episodes.title: Drinking and Driving

episodes.synopsis: Zack thinks he's negotiated a great deal with slimy ring salesman Gem Diamond for class rings.
episodes.title: Class Rings

episodes.synopsis: An alumni of Bayside leaves money to the school via a will.
episodes.title: The Will

episodes.synopsis: Slater's sister J.B. comes to town to visit and Zack wants to date her.
episodes.title: Slater's Sister

episodes.synopsis: During an earthquake, Tori, Zack and Mrs. Belding get trapped in the faculty elevator.
episodes.title: Earthquake

episodes.synopsis: This compilation features clips from the Malibu Sands episodes.
episodes.title: The Best Summer of My Life

episodes.synopsis: The kids want to leave their mark on Bayside and decide to have a contest to come up with a new school song.
episodes.title: School Song
